el poema épico sacro, la dilucidación de una sermocinatio de san Isidro a la luz de las reglas de la predicación áureo secular, la contaminación de modelos literarios que sustenta la configuración del personaje de Santa María de la Cabeza en el Isidro. Poema castellano y las relaciones entre visualidad, iconografía y tratamiento teatral en las piezas dedicadas al patrón de Madrid.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / Spanish & Portuguese.2bisacsh1 aCárdenas, Jesús Ponce, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGutiérrez, Esther Borrego, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLosada, Manuel José Crespo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aParrado, Pedro Conde, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPonce Cárdenas, Jesús, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRodríguez, Natalia Fernández, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2021z9783110753899oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertVervuert Complete eBook-Package 2021z9783110743340oZDB-207-IBV40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869178740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968691787423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968691787/original  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-207-IBVb2021  aZDB-23-DKUb2021